I"€<h3 id="why-do-you-need-action">Why do you need action?</h3>
<p>Workflow is capable of generating action by placing an action node directly on the workflow canvas. The Actions are generally used 
to notify something to the someone or perform a special activity. In case of workflow of 
APPSeCONNECT, there is a number of actions that you can perform while executing the workflow.</p>
